                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a>&nbsp;3 月 5 日消息，AOC 旗下“25G10HE”24.5&nbsp;英寸显示器现已在京东首销，其主打“1080P 200Hz”，<strong>定价为&nbsp;649&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/GaU3HZM" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/268216/9/24652/69948/67beb386Fae60a7ba/fafc781f42f553c4.jpg" title="AOC“25G10HE”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 200Hz 超频，649 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> AOC“25G10HE”显示器</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 649 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2616" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/3/30b542f2-ce5b-4c02-9adb-0012dcae6353.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC“25G10HE”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 200Hz 超频，649 元" width="744" /></p><p>据介绍，这款显示器配备&nbsp;1920x1080&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;200Hz（超频）Fast IPS&nbsp;面板，显示器典型亮度&nbsp;300&nbsp;尼特，MPRT&nbsp;响应速度&nbsp;0.3ms，静态对比度&nbsp;1000:1，显示器支持&nbsp;8-Bit&nbsp;色彩，覆盖&nbsp;99% sRGB&nbsp;和&nbsp;90% DCI-P3&nbsp;色域。</p><p>这款显示器支架支持倾斜，显示器本体支持&nbsp;VESA 100x100mm&nbsp;壁挂，提供&nbsp;2&nbsp;个 HDMI 2.0、1&nbsp;个 DP 1.4、1&nbsp;个 3.5mm&nbsp;音频接口。</p><p>IT之家附显示器参数信息如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="900" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/3/7ec255e7-5d2f-44c0-85b2-4fad1ec929ab.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC“25G10HE”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 200Hz 超频，649 元" width="732" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1284" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/3/e7bc97c5-e500-4c95-a9cb-76382aa6c19a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="AOC“25G10HE”24.5 英寸显示器首销：1080P 200Hz 超频，649 元" width="740" /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式